[
  {
    "startTime": 3.837,
    "endTime": 5.104,
    "text": "So what do you want\r\nto do tonight?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.137,
    "endTime": 6.773,
    "text": "Like, I was thinking\r\nmaybe we could meet up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.806,
    "endTime": 8.441,
    "text": "with Amy and Brad,\r\nand, like, before that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.474,
    "endTime": 10.043,
    "text": "we could go to Angela's,\r\nand before that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.076,
    "endTime": 11.31,
    "text": "we could, like, just go--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.343,
    "endTime": 13.78,
    "text": "Meegan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.813,
    "endTime": 15.782,
    "text": "I have something\r\nto say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.017,
    "endTime": 19.185,
    "text": "[exhales sharply]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.218,
    "endTime": 21.02,
    "text": "I had to say it\r\nin person"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.053,
    "endTime": 24.758000000000003,
    "text": "because it's--\r\nit's, like, super important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.859,
    "endTime": 29.662000000000003,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.695,
    "endTime": 31.497,
    "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.53,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "I know this is sudden,\r\nbut, like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.033,
    "endTime": 37.336,
    "text": "I've been thinking\r\nabout this for a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.369,
    "endTime": 41.307,
    "text": "And I know this is something\r\nthat needs to happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.34,
    "endTime": 42.675000000000004,
    "text": "I'm breaking up\r\nwith you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.708,
    "endTime": 44.177,
    "text": "Cool.\r\nLove it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.21,
    "endTime": 46.279,
    "text": "Totally fine\r\nwith that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.182,
    "endTime": 52.318000000000005,
    "text": "- R-Really?\r\n- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.351,
    "endTime": 54.519999999999996,
    "text": "'Cause I thought--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.553,
    "endTime": 55.988,
    "text": "I was really worried"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.021,
    "endTime": 58.558,
    "text": "that you were\r\ngonna be, like, mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.591,
    "endTime": 60.426,
    "text": "Mad?\r\nOh, my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.459,
    "endTime": 61.994,
    "text": "Are you kidding me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.027,
    "endTime": 64.56400000000001,
    "text": "No, of course\r\nI'm not mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.597,
    "endTime": 66.232,
    "text": "People grow apart.\r\nIt happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.265,
    "endTime": 67.5,
    "text": "It's, like,\r\npart of life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.533,
    "endTime": 68.734,
    "text": "No, I'm totally fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.767,
    "endTime": 72.00399999999999,
    "text": "Like, love it,\r\nlove it, love it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.037,
    "endTime": 74.373,
    "text": "Um...\r\n[clears throat]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.406,
    "endTime": 76.876,
    "text": "So..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.909,
    "endTime": 78.51100000000001,
    "text": "Uh, um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.544,
    "endTime": 80.847,
    "text": "we had a good run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.88,
    "endTime": 81.881,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.185,
    "endTime": 88.855,
    "text": "And, uh, don't be\r\na stranger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.888,
    "endTime": 91.491,
    "text": "Can I just--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.524,
    "endTime": 93.593,
    "text": "Can I ask why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.626,
    "endTime": 95.89500000000001,
    "text": "- Why?\r\n- Yeah, like, whatevs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.928,
    "endTime": 97.53,
    "text": "Like, I'm doing some work\r\non myself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.563,
    "endTime": 99.165,
    "text": "and, like, trying to grow\r\nas a person,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.198,
    "endTime": 102.101,
    "text": "so I'd really, like,\r\nappreciate to know why."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.134,
    "endTime": 103.736,
    "text": "Yeah, um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.769,
    "endTime": 105.471,
    "text": "Okay, yeah,\r\nthat's, like--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.504,
    "endTime": 107.84,
    "text": "You know, I think\r\nthat you're kind of, like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.873,
    "endTime": 110.07600000000001,
    "text": "a controlling\r\nperson who--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.109,
    "endTime": 111.44399999999999,
    "text": "Thank you.\r\nThank you for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.477,
    "endTime": 114.41300000000001,
    "text": "That's nice.\r\nThank you for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.446,
    "endTime": 116.115,
    "text": "Cool.\r\nNo problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.148,
    "endTime": 118.317,
    "text": "So you know what\r\nyour problem is, Andre?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.35,
    "endTime": 119.51899999999999,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.552,
    "endTime": 122.622,
    "text": "You keep tabs\r\non people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.655,
    "endTime": 124.023,
    "text": "Every little thing\r\nsomebody does,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.056,
    "endTime": 127.593,
    "text": "you have to keep\r\na tab of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.626,
    "endTime": 130.596,
    "text": "Wait. I-I can't tell\r\nif you're angry or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.629,
    "endTime": 131.731,
    "text": "I'm not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.764,
    "endTime": 134.10000000000002,
    "text": "Mm, totally not angry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.133,
    "endTime": 135.334,
    "text": "No, I'm excited.\r\nIt's good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.367,
    "endTime": 137.57,
    "text": "It's just, like,\r\nyou said your piece,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.603,
    "endTime": 141.073,
    "text": "and I just think\r\nthat I deserve the human decency"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.106,
    "endTime": 142.475,
    "text": "to say my piece."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.508,
    "endTime": 143.50900000000001,
    "text": "Right, right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.542,
    "endTime": 145.611,
    "text": "Is that--\r\nis that not okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.644,
    "endTime": 147.88,
    "text": "No, no, no.\r\nIt's--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.913,
    "endTime": 150.049,
    "text": "Of course, of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.082,
    "endTime": 151.851,
    "text": "You're a controlling,\r\nmanipulative person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.884,
    "endTime": 153.219,
    "text": "Everyone says that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.252,
    "endTime": 154.72,
    "text": "I-I don't think\r\nthat I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.753,
    "endTime": 156.72199999999998,
    "text": "Yes, you are, Andre."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.755,
    "endTime": 160.52599999999998,
    "text": "Yes, you motherfucking are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.559,
    "endTime": 162.695,
    "text": "Okay, now--now,\r\nyou sound pretty angry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.728,
    "endTime": 164.931,
    "text": "I'm not angry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.964,
    "endTime": 167.033,
    "text": "I'm not angry.\r\nI'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.066,
    "endTime": 168.034,
    "text": "I love it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.067,
    "endTime": 169.40200000000002,
    "text": "I love that you came\r\nto my house,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.435,
    "endTime": 171.237,
    "text": "and you broke up with me\r\nin my space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.27,
    "endTime": 173.239,
    "text": "And I'm gonna think about that\r\nevery time I'm here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.272,
    "endTime": 174.807,
    "text": "That's great.\r\nThat is so perfect for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.84,
    "endTime": 177.076,
    "text": "[crying]\r\nIt's the best thing\r\nthat's ever happened to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.109,
    "endTime": 178.411,
    "text": "Where else was\r\nI supposed to do it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.444,
    "endTime": 179.74499999999998,
    "text": "'Cause you won't come\r\nto my house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.778,
    "endTime": 182.582,
    "text": "Oh, here he is.\r\nThe puppet master is back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.615,
    "endTime": 184.317,
    "text": "But I'm not--\r\nNo, I'm not the puppet master."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.35,
    "endTime": 185.718,
    "text": "Why are you\r\ndoing this to me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.751,
    "endTime": 187.286,
    "text": "It's true.\r\nYou won't come to my house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.319,
    "endTime": 188.988,
    "text": "You said my apartment\r\nlooks like two rats"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.021,
    "endTime": 190.523,
    "text": "just shit in it\r\nevery fucking day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.556,
    "endTime": 192.525,
    "text": "Oh, right,\r\nlike, thank you for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.558,
    "endTime": 193.826,
    "text": "I'm a bitch.\r\nThank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.859,
    "endTime": 195.36100000000002,
    "text": "I didn't call--\r\nno, I didn't say \"bitch.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.394,
    "endTime": 196.46200000000002,
    "text": "- I didn't--\r\n- Which is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.495,
    "endTime": 197.797,
    "text": "Am I evil,\r\nor am I a bitch?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.83,
    "endTime": 199.098,
    "text": "No, no, you're\r\nnot evil, Meegan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.131,
    "endTime": 200.9,
    "text": "Well, then why\r\nare you punishing me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.933,
    "endTime": 202.935,
    "text": "I'm not punishing you.\r\nI'm not--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.968,
    "endTime": 204.10299999999998,
    "text": "You broke up with me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.136,
    "endTime": 205.638,
    "text": "and I'm not supposed\r\nto feel punished."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.671,
    "endTime": 208.07399999999998,
    "text": "- Who thinks like that?\r\n- [shouting]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.107,
    "endTime": 210.109,
    "text": "I don't know!\r\nI'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.142,
    "endTime": 211.877,
    "text": "I'm sorry,\r\nokay, Meegan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.91,
    "endTime": 213.412,
    "text": "I guess I didn't think\r\nit through."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.445,
    "endTime": 214.74699999999999,
    "text": "Well, it's, like,\r\ntoo late now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.78,
    "endTime": 216.649,
    "text": "- I mean, we're done.\r\n- No, it's not too late."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.682,
    "endTime": 218.851,
    "text": "Meegan, Meegan,\r\nseriously, I just--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.884,
    "endTime": 222.255,
    "text": "I-I-I had a feeling\r\nthat I thought was true,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.288,
    "endTime": 224.59,
    "text": "and clearly--\r\nclearly it wasn't true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.623,
    "endTime": 226.759,
    "text": "Like, I'm so confused."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.792,
    "endTime": 228.094,
    "text": "Like, are you\r\nbreaking up with me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.127,
    "endTime": 229.428,
    "text": "or are you not\r\nbreaking up with me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.461,
    "endTime": 232.23100000000002,
    "text": "Meegan, I'm not\r\nbreaking up with you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.264,
    "endTime": 234.066,
    "text": "Okay, cool. So what do you want\r\nto do tonight?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.099,
    "endTime": 235.66799999999998,
    "text": "Like, I want to hang out\r\nwith Amy and Brad,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.701,
    "endTime": 237.536,
    "text": "but maybe before that,\r\nwe can go to Angela's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.569,
    "endTime": 240.539,
    "text": "[dark music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.572,
    "endTime": 241.941,
    "text": "♪ ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.974,
    "endTime": 243.91,
    "text": "What just happened?"
  }
]